# Brand and Styling Guide

- Maintain the dark theme baseline: `bg-dark-950`, `text-dark-100`, muted text with `text-dark-400/500`.
- Use the `Inter` font family; do not introduce new fonts.
- Prefer consistent rounded corners and soft shadows (`rounded-lg`, `shadow-card`).
- Primary actions use the existing `btn-primary` styling and `primary-600/700` palette.
- Secondary actions use `btn-secondary` and dark palette classes.
- Keep spacing consistent with current layouts (gap-3/4/6, padding 4/6).
